<section class="page-hero" style="height:40vh;min-height:280px;">
  <div class="page-hero__bg">
    <div class="page-hero__bg-placeholder"></div>
    <div class="page-hero__overlay"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="page-hero__content">
      <p class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom:1rem;">— Our Promise</p>
      <h1 style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:clamp(2.5rem,6vw,5rem);color:var(--white);">Shipping &amp; Returns</h1>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section class="page-body">
  <div class="container">
    <div style="max-width:48rem;">
      <div class="policy-card">
        <h3>Shipping</h3>
        <div class="policy-card__item">
          <p class="policy-card__q">How much is shipping?</p>
          <p class="policy-card__a">Completely free on every order, worldwide. No minimum purchase required.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="policy-card__item">
          <p class="policy-card__q">How long does delivery take?</p>
          <p class="policy-card__a">US: 3–5 business days. Canada & Europe: 5–10 days. Rest of world: 7–14 days. Express shipping $9.99 (1–3 days in US).</p>
        </div>
        <div class="policy-card__item">
          <p class="policy-card__q">Do you provide tracking?</p>
          <p class="policy-card__a">Yes — every order ships with a tracking number sent via email within 24 hours of dispatch.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="policy-card">
        <h3>Returns & Refunds</h3>
        <div class="policy-card__item">
          <p class="policy-card__q">What is your return policy?</p>
          <p class="policy-card__a">30-day no-questions-asked returns. Not satisfied? Ship it back for a full refund.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="policy-card__item">
          <p class="policy-card__q">Who pays for return shipping?</p>
          <p class="policy-card__a">We do. We'll provide a prepaid return label — your satisfaction means everything.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="policy-card__item">
          <p class="policy-card__q">How long until I get my refund?</p>
          <p class="policy-card__a">Refunds are processed within 3–5 business days of receiving your return.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="policy-card">
        <h3>Quality Guarantee</h3>
        <div class="policy-card__item">
          <p class="policy-card__q">What are your products made of?</p>
          <p class="policy-card__a">All pieces are crafted from surgical-grade 316L stainless steel — hypoallergenic, waterproof, and tarnish-resistant. Built to last a lifetime.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="policy-card__item">
          <p class="policy-card__q">What if my bracelet breaks?</p>
          <p class="policy-card__a">We offer a lifetime replacement guarantee. If your piece ever breaks under normal wear, we'll send a replacement free of charge.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="policy-card">
        <h3>Contact Us</h3>
        <div class="policy-card__item">
          <p class="policy-card__q">How can I reach support?</p>
          <p class="policy-card__a">Email hello@radioactivelove.com — we respond within 24 hours. DM us on Instagram @radioactivelove.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
{% schema %}{"name":"Policies Page","settings":[]}{% endschema %}